SUMMARY:Free GED Practice Testing
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/free-ged-practice-testing-ticket
 s-56514296783\n\nWondering if you're ready to take your GED tests? Come 
 find out!Take up to 3 GED Ready official practice tests for FREE at Roan
 oke Valley - Alleghany Region 5 Adult Education's Free Test Friday on Ma
 rch 1st at the Roanoke Higher Education Center. Anyone 18 years or older
 \, and not currently enrolled in a Region 5 GED class\, is welcome to co
 me test for FREE!Practice tests will be offered from 9:00AM - 11:30AM an
 d 1:00PM - 4:00PM. Register and select the session you're interested in 
 to reserve your spot. Call 1-888-622-7256 or visitwww.regionfiveadulted.
 comfor more information.
